		(uuid "e71ab896-4ca1-4fdf-86c8-c089a8e16487")
		(at 112.5 73.5)
		(descr "Shun Xiang Nuo SMNR4020 magnetic-resin shielded SMD power inductor, 4.0 x 4.0 x 2.0 mm. L1 = SMNR4020-2.2UH (LCSC C135262): 2.2uH +/-20%, Isat 3.4 A, DCR 46 mohm. Land pattern per SXN datasheet: F=0.95 (pad length), G=2.1 (pad width), H=3.3 (outer span) -> pads 0.95 x 2.1 mm at +/-1.175 mm. SIZED FOR THE 1.50 A STARTUP INRUSH measured in LTspice with TI's TPS61023 model -- NOT the 0.54 A steady-state current. Do not substitute a 3x3 part.")
